    "description": "HemoMIPs-Automated analysis and result reporting pipeline for targeted sequencing data.\n\nThe hemoMIPs pipeline is a fast and efficient analysis pipeline for the analysis of multiplexed and targeted NGS datasets created from Molecular Inversion Probes (MIPs). It runs highly automated using conda und snakemake and can be set to use GATK v4 or GATK v3 for variant calling. It reports benign and likely pathogenic variants in a userfriendly HTML report that shows detailed performance statistics and results.",
